| 4 | LOW | `import re` and `from ..tools import create_thing` placed inside function body in `gmail.py`, inconsistent with `calendar.py` which puts them at module level |

**Positives**: `Promise.allSettled` handles partial failures gracefully, `create_thing` deduplication prevents re-seed pollution, `user_filter_clause` correctly used in new-user query, both `run()`/`run_stream()` consistently updated.
